OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAreas of cloud for the morning
OL,6,Fand at first in the afternoon, then
OL,7,Fmost places gradually becoming sunny.
OL,8,FRather warm for most places, highest
OL,9,Ftemperatures across Hampshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMainly clear skies to start
OL,12,Fthe evening, becoming cloudy at times
OL,13,Fespecially along the coast. Winds
OL,14,Flight northwesterly but breezy along
OL,15,Fthe coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA dry and sunny start,
OL,18,Fbecoming cloudy during the morning,
OL,19,Fovernight skies clear except along the
OL,20,Fcoast where the cloud lingers. Winds
OL,21,Fbecoming light and variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
