OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FRemaining very warm with light winds.
OL,7,FProbably cloudy at times Tuesday and
OL,8,FWednesday, with potential for a few
OL,9,Fshowers on Thursday.
